page.title: 05BOY SCOUTS
page.content: The name of the Scouts is Ospreys.The games we play are rounders,football, slipper,basketball,colditz and getting across the beams.The uniform you have to wear is a Scouts hat,black socks and black shoes,a jumper or a shirt,a scarf,black or grey trousers.You must not wear black trainers.You can get your uniform from Fambridge Road, Maldon, Essex.Our leader is Shawn Southerland,he lives at number 28, Ramsey Chase, Latchingdon, Essex.When we go camping we go canoeing,swimming,playing games and having a camp fire and water fights.Nearly every Saturday we can go canoeing down the bay you have to go to 205,North Drive, Maylandsea, Essex.
